  "name": "Manage Your JetSend Accounts",
  "body": "<p>You can view and update your account details in the ACCOUNT(S) tab of the Account Details page. Click your user name on the top-right corner of the application and from the drop-down menu, select Account Settings. Then, on the Account Details page, select the ACCOUNT(S) tab.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"User-added image\" height=\"643\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountsTab.05T5g00000Gk1lTEAR.png\" width=\"699\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 643px; width: 699px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountsTab.05T5g00000Gk1lTEAR.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountsTab.05T5g00000Gk1lTEAR.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountsTab.05T5g00000Gk1lTEAR.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountsTab.05T5g00000Gk1lTEAR.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountsTab.05T5g00000Gk1lTEAR.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountsTab.05T5g00000Gk1lTEAR.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountsTab.05T5g00000Gk1lTEAR.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/> </p>\n<h2 data-id=\"manage-company-information\">Manage Company Information</h2>\n<p>The 'Your Company Information' section in the ACCOUNT(S) tab is where you can update your company details such as company name, address, and contact number.<br/><br/> </p>\n<h2 data-id=\"manage-sub-accounts\">Manage Sub-Accounts</h2>\n<p>The <b>Accounts</b> section in the <b>ACCOUNT(S)</b> tab displays all the sub-accounts that are associated with your primary account. Here, you can see the account information (such as name and status) and edit the account name. To learn about the Multi-Account feature, see <a href=\"\">Multi-Account Management</a>.<br/><br/>You can add as many sub-accounts as you want. Click the <b>Add Account</b> button. Next, on the <b>Add Account</b> dialog box, enter the name of the account that you want to add and then click <b>Save</b>.<br/><img alt=\"User-added image\" height=\"213\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AddAccount.05T5g00000Gk1uuEAB.png\" width=\"424\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 213px; width: 424px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AddAccount.05T5g00000Gk1uuEAB.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AddAccount.05T5g00000Gk1uuEAB.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AddAccount.05T5g00000Gk1uuEAB.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AddAccount.05T5g00000Gk1uuEAB.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AddAccount.05T5g00000Gk1uuEAB.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AddAccount.05T5g00000Gk1uuEAB.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AddAccount.05T5g00000Gk1uuEAB.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>",
